OL,3,CPrince Harry considers not bringing
OL,4,Cfamily on UK trip
OL,6,FPrince Harry is considering leaving
OL,7,Fhis wife and children at home in
OL,8,FCalifornia when he comes to the UK
OL,9,Fnext week, despite pledging to bring
OL,10,Fthem to his home country for the first
OL,11,Ftime in many years.
OL,13,FThe Duke of Sussex is blaming the
OL,14,Fongoing arguments over his security
OL,15,Farrangements and is accusing those in
OL,16,Fcharge of going back on their word.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
