OL,3,CPrince Harry considers not bringing
OL,4,Cfamily on UK trip
OL,6,FHarry is due to attend a number of
OL,7,Fcharity engagements next week, which
OL,8,Fincludes marking the one year to go
OL,9,Funtil the Invictus Games in Birmingham
OL,10,Fin 2027.
OL,12,FIn a surprise move, his office had
OL,13,Fpreviously said Meghan and the
OL,14,Fcouple's children, Archie and Lilibet,
OL,15,Fwould be coming with them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
