OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782690475
OL,3,CPrince Harry considers not bringing
OL,4,Cfamily on UK trip
OL,6,FKing Charles has not seen his
OL,7,Fgrandchildren since they visited
OL,8,FLondon for the late Queen's Platinum
OL,9,FJubilee in 2022 and Meghan has not
OL,10,Fbeen to the UK since Queen Elizabeth's
OL,11,Ffuneral in the September of that year.
OL,13,FPrince Harry's automatic security
OL,14,Fprotection was removed when he left
OL,15,Fthe Royal Family and moved to the USA
OL,16,Fand he has since claimed it is not
OL,17,Fsafe to bring his family to his
OL,18,Fcountry of birth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
