OL,3,CPrince Harry considers not bringing
OL,4,Cfamily on UK trip
OL,6,FSenior staff in the Sussexes' office
OL,7,Fsay there are multiple threats to
OL,8,Ftarget Harry and the online abuse
OL,9,Fdirected at his wife, makes her
OL,10,Fvulnerable to an attack when she is in
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,FThe committee in charge of royal
OL,14,Fsecurity, known as RAVEC, ruled that
OL,15,Fthe Duke and his family should not get
OL,16,Ftaxpayer-funded security but Harry has
OL,17,Falways claimed the decisions were
OL,18,Finfluenced by those working for the
OL,19,FRoyal Family, rather than on security
OL,20,Fgrounds alone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
