OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782690475
OL,3,CPrince Harry considers not bringing
OL,4,Cfamily on UK trip
OL,6,FThe Duke of Sussex says he is aware of
OL,7,Fmultiple threats against him,
OL,8,Fincluding death threats, and despite
OL,9,Fbeing given high-level security when
OL,10,Fhe's travelled to places like Ukraine,
OL,11,FColombia and Nigeria, he is only
OL,12,Foffered the phone number of a police
OL,13,Fliaison officer when he travels to
OL,14,FBritain.
OL,16,FWhile Harry and Meghan pay for their
OL,17,Fown security personnel, as many
OL,18,Fcelebrities do, they do not get access
OL,19,Fto state-level intelligence from MI5
OL,20,Fand MI6 like officers do in the
OL,21,FMetropolitan Police and other forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
