OL,3,CPrince Harry considers not bringing
OL,4,Cfamily on UK trip
OL,6,FSources in Harry's team say that is a
OL,7,Fbizarre decision given he is the son
OL,8,Fof the Monarch and remains fifth in
OL,9,Fline to the throne and his children
OL,10,Fare sixth and seventh in the line of
OL,11,Fsuccession.
OL,13,FHarry's staff also point to the fact
OL,14,Fthat high profile celebrities like
OL,15,FTaylor Swift get state-funded security
OL,16,Fbecause of the threats against her,
OL,17,Fbut he does not.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
