OL,3,CPrince Harry considers not bringing
OL,4,Cfamily on UK trip
OL,6,FSources at Buckingham Palace will not
OL,7,Fcomment on security arrangements but
OL,8,Fhave confirmed they offered for Harry
OL,9,Fand Meghan to stay at a royal
OL,10,Fresidence during their stay in the UK.
OL,12,FThey claim that offer has not been
OL,13,Faccepted by the Sussexes.
OL,15,FThose in Harry's camp claim they were
OL,16,Fpromised a new Risk Management Board
OL,17,Fby the RAVEC Committee, but it has not
OL,18,Fbeen carried out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
