PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782690475
OL,3,CPrince Harry considers not bringing
OL,4,Cfamily on UK trip
OL,6,FThey have once again blamed the "grey
OL,7,Fsuits" in the palace - referring to
OL,8,Fthe senior staff around the King,
OL,9,Frather than the King himself.
OL,11,FSources close to Prince Harry say 3 of
OL,12,Fthe nine members of the RAVEC Board -
OL,13,F(so one third) are made up of staff
OL,14,Ffrom Buckingham Palace and Prince
OL,15,FWilliam's office - and suggest that is
OL,16,Fthe real reason Harry is not being
OL,17,Foffered a security review.
OL,19,FPrince Harry is now understood to be
OL,20,Fdeciding whether it is safe to being
OL,21,Fhis wife and children with him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
